{"tid":1687021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"維園明辦選舉聚會 警提醒：可能出水炮車","createTime":"2019-11-01T14:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T14:46:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba988a8e676348179daff3718c84450586e653a","tid":1687021,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"明日（2日）的維園集會被警方禁止，但另外同日在遮打花園及愛丁堡廣場的集會已獲警方發不反對通知書，亦有128名民主派區議會候選人正積極考慮於維園舉辦選舉聚會。維園集會不反對通知書申請人劉頴匡呼籲市民明日參與集會，向國際展示港人仍未妥協、民意未有逆轉。警方今日（1日）向區議員發出信息，提醒明日有可能用水炮車，通知他們安排。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf43c10b21ada02a21ffe2dc7f3ecbde93b7b46","tid":1687021,"uid":231766,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"你老婆咪水砲車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ef57cc2e670f9248c9b86976a58dac4e03e5a7","tid":1687021,"uid":14422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"你老婆咪水砲車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a843376b0c4a85dfc6960e348ca9dbdc16a8aa61","tid":1687021,"uid":184500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"甴帝 甴大大 甴曱平"},{"pid":"a2354049c0b9f08e15c5e77b075a8cd5c2352f48","tid":1687021,"uid":288707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"你老婆咪水砲車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062e4ba9ee44a30ad5bdc27a2e81462fcd55a9f6","tid":1687021,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"【長期置頂】11.2行動po合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1687004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1687004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42bfe92b44b4fceee0aa1a4002d39a9c1941e9bf","tid":1687021,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"叫啲狗乸出嚟做咩？"},{"pid":"5dd